{"tid":1297256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通宵唱聖詩嘅主辦[時代論壇]，所屬記者被警方粗暴對待","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:52:28.000Z","uid":154702,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"430266d5d6fa547a2cce3565b2316f7d1b1719e8","tid":1297256,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"當晚帶頭唱聖詩既基督教主辦單位[時代論壇]<br />\n所屬記者都有被黑警推跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【時代論壇嚴正聲明】<br />\n<br />\n本報攝影記者鄭樂天在七月七日深夜採訪旺角彌敦道清場時，遭到警務人員粗暴對待，推跌在地，阻礙採訪，且被誣捏襲警。這是繼六月十二日金鐘清場以來，本報記者再度遇到同類事件，而且情況比第一次更嚴重，記者並無身體損傷，實屬萬幸。本報對此深表憤怒，嚴正譴責警方侵犯新聞自由之舉，並對警方月來未有改善，表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府領導層月來多番錯誤，迴避數以百萬市民訴求，造成社會氣氛繃緊，警隊亦成磨心。然而，警務人員手執公權力，處事必須保持克制公允，尊重新聞自由及採訪權利，這是香港作為文明社會的合理期望；警隊領導層在內部重塑尊重自律的文化和工作方式，更屬責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n基督教時代論壇有限公司<br />\n2019年7月8日</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=158725&amp;Pid=102&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2186&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FCommon%2FReader%2FNews%2FShowNews.jsp%3FNid%3D158725%26Pid%3D102%26Version%3D0%26Cid%3D2186%26Charset%3Dbig5_hkscs&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUhkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=9a817564\" target=\"_blank\">https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=158725&amp;Pid=102&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2186&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs</a>"},{"pid":"c9cfe5430bfed235cf702e276eb6aefe96c8b2d9","tid":1297256,"uid":47905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"人神共憤<br />\n所以係時候搞遊行反警"},{"pid":"63490381f4c8f432b1980b5ee28ce4dcd2c46da5","tid":1297256,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:0